    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/01/125391187/47817b4476bcd8b44c86c87debf042f2_1979164307304698094.png",
                "id": "talent19963",
                "key": "鐮刀旋斬",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "鐮刀旋斬"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">水元素傷害</span>。</p><p>如果有敵方角色附屬有<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">凍結</span>或<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">水泡圍困</span>，則本角色獲得1點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">充能</span>。（每回合1次）</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">凍結</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">角色無法使用技能。</span>（持續到回合結束）</p><p>角色受到<span style=\"color: #FF9999\">火元素傷害</span>或<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>時，移除此效果，使該傷害+2。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">水泡圍困</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">角色無法使用技能。</span>（持續到回合結束）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/01/125391187/2139cdf27302ec3978e3ef0ec9730400_8847075070944494767.png",
                "id": "talent24646",
                "key": "狂瀾鐮擊",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "狂瀾鐮擊"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素傷害</span>，生成手牌<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">水泡史萊姆</span>。</p><p>（裝備有<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">水泡史萊姆</span>的角色可以使用特技：<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">水泡戰法</span>）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/01/125391187/28dd7cbc401fba1847d124b593b37cc2_78084254522415411.png",
                "id": "talent68959",
                "key": "浮泡攻勢",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "浮泡攻勢"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">特技</span></p><p>(需準備1個行動輪)造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素傷害</span>，敵方出戰角色附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">水泡圍困</span>。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">水泡圍困</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">角色無法使用技能。</span>（持續到回合結束）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/01/125391187/b129887ff77afc4936437b276dd6e645_5718863278134807233.png",
                "id": "talent57694",
                "key": "水泡戰法",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "white"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "水泡戰法"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">裝備牌</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">特技</span>：水泡戰法</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：2</span></p><p>（角色最多裝備1個「特技」）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/01/125391187/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7569977200849490131.png",
                "id": "talent73577",
                "key": "水泡史萊姆",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/01/125391187/47f0e77e4279d21ba6bb0062db34d677_8916027952418924483.png",
                "title": "水泡史萊姆"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸發</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感電</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">凍結</span>：本傷害+1，使目標本回合無法行動（受到<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>傷害後提前解除，但是傷害+2）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">綻放</span>：本傷害+1，生成使下次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>傷害+2的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「草原核」</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">草原核</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方對敵方出戰角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>時，傷害值+2。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/01/125391187/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_4347250699023079347.png",
                "id": "talent93446",
                "key": "水元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "水元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸發</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超載</span>：本傷害+2，目標強制切換到下一個角色</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/01/125391187/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_4957569943430990368.png",
                "key": "火元素傷害‧其一",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "火元素傷害‧其一"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒</span>：本傷害+1，召喚<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒烈焰</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\"><br></span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒烈焰</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1，最多叠加到2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/01/125391187/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_3354517979086398064.png",
                "key": "火元素傷害‧其二",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/01/125391187/3c3362a64ac984342133762388c9eb41_780322457868358499.png",
                "title": "火元素傷害‧其二"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">充能</span></p><p>角色使用「元素爆發」時，需要消耗 充能。</p><p>角色使用「元素戰技」或「普通攻擊」後，會獲得1點充能。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">特技</span></p><p>出戰角色裝備有「特技」卡牌時，就可以使用對應的「特技」。</p><p>使用「特技」是一種「戰鬥行動」。角色因凍結、石化、眩暈等原因無法使用技能時，也會同時無法使用「特技」。</p><p>角色使用「特技」時不視為使用技能，無法觸發「使用技能後」、「角色引發元素反應後」等效果；角色使用「特技」造成的傷害不視為角色造成的傷害。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/01/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_1700108590385390375.png",
